message.content:
Kia ora! Ka whakararuraru ahau ki ngā whakatau ā-iwi mā te whakatau i tētahi tauira ako mīhini. Ka āwhina ahau i a koe ki te whakatutuki i ēnei whakararuraru. Tuhi mai i āu pātai i te reo Māori, ā, ka whakautu ahau ki ēnei pātai i te reo Māori hoki.

1. Ka whakararuraru ahau i te whakatau ā-iwi. Ka whakaae ahau ki te āwhina i a koe. Ka taea e koe te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i tēnei?

2. He aha te āhua o te whakararuraru? Ka āwhina ahau ki te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i tēnei whakararuraru.

3. Ka whakararuraru ahau ki te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i ngā whakatau ā-iwi. Ka āwhina ahau i a koe ki te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i ēnei whakatau ā-iwi.

4. Ka whakaae ahau ki te whakawhitiwhiti īmēra ki a koe. Ka taea e koe te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i ēnei īmēra.

5. Ka whakararuru ahau ki te whakatutuki i ngā kōrero whakararuraru. Ka āwhina ahau i a koe ki te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki i ēnei kōrero whakarararu.

Whakautu mai ki ēnei pātai ki te reo Māori, ā, ka āwhina ahau i a koe ki te whakapau kaha ki te whakatutuki
